  "remarks": "\nMr Marzouk is a senior Hamas official and has been the deputy leader of Hamas since 1997. He has publicly represented the proscribed military wing of Hamas. He has been involved in terrorist financing and has defended Hamas’ terrorist activity, including the targeting of civilians.",
